# Do Not Change UI

**Never modify the UI of this project.** This includes:

- React components (JSX/TSX)
- CSS, Tailwind classes, or styling
- Layout, structure, or visual design
- Component appearance or behavior that affects what users see

Only make changes to non-UI code (logic, config, tooling, backend, etc.) unless explicitly asked to change UI.
